CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 10, 1958, pg. A18 reads: "BPW Winners - Three of the five babies who took prizes offered by the Business and Professional Women's baby contest at the Greene Hearthe recently are, left to right: Paul Eugene Acie, first-prize winner; William H. Davis III, second, and Keith L. Johnson, who holds the certificate which his sister, Lynn, shares for third-place honors, with Hubert P. Davis. Jean Renee Fowler, not in picture, took the final prize. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of winners Paul Eugene Acie, William H. Davis III, and Keith L. Johnson, seated on table in the Greene Hearth for the Business and Professional Women's baby contest
